*Story*
Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey on a jamun tree, which was on the bank of a river.In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife.
One day, the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree. The monkey offered some fruits. The crocodile came back next day for more fruits,
as he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became good freinds.
